des:
'Starship Sounds: Ambient Engine Noise' provides a calming high-quality engine sound on loop so it will sound like you are living in the Captain's quarters!

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Starship Sounds" or "Alexa, play Starship Sounds" to start the engine.
At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop".

Audio Credit: https://cheesynirvosa.bandcamp.com/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
